---
<section class="py-24 px-6 relative">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="font-['Playfair_Display'] text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 tracking-tight">
        The Gap Between <span class="italic text-orange-500">Generation</span> and <span class="italic text-orange-500">Selection</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-white/40 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-base leading-relaxed">
        AI creates content in seconds. Choosing the best of it still takes hours.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12">
      <!-- Problem -->
      <div class="glass-card p-8 border-red-500/20 group hover:border-red-500/30 transition-all duration-700">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-red-500/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="rgb(239 68 68)" stroke-width="2">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
              <line x1="15" y1="9" x2="9" y2="15"></line>
              <line x1="9" y1="9" x2="15" y2="15"></line>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-['Playfair_Display'] text-2xl font-semibold">The Problem</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Teams fall into two traps when AI-generated content floods their pipeline:
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-red-500/5 border border-red-500/10">
            <span class="text-red-400 text-sm font-semibold block mb-1">Over-adoption</span>
            <span class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Ship everything, quality collapses. Brand erosion, revision loops, wasted production budget.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-red-500/5 border border-red-500/10">
            <span class="text-red-400 text-sm font-semibold block mb-1">Under-adoption</span>
            <span class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Review too slowly, miss the speed advantage. Competitors ship while you're still picking favorites.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Solution -->
      <div class="glass-card p-8 border-green-500/20 group hover:border-green-500/30 transition-all duration-700">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-green-500/10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="rgb(34 197 94)" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path>
              <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-['Playfair_Display'] text-2xl font-semibold">The Solution</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Wabbit closes the gap with gesture-driven ranking that matches the speed of AI generation.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-green-500/5 border border-green-500/10">
            <span class="text-green-400 text-sm font-semibold block mb-1">200 assets in 2 minutes</span>
            <span class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Swipe-based scoring parses hundreds of generations in minutes, not hours. No clicking, no star ratings.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-green-500/5 border border-green-500/10">
            <span class="text-green-400 text-sm font-semibold block mb-1">Team consensus, not opinions</span>
            <span class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">RAVG (Ranked Average) aggregates team input into a single weighted score. Best content surfaces automatically.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
